item.title: SoftLayer_Billing_Invoice_Tax_Info
item.description: SoftLayer_Billing_Invoice_Tax_Info Datatype Description Invoice tax information contains top-level information about the taxes recorded for a particular invoice. Local createDate The date and time this tax information was recorded. Type: dateTime currencyId The currency code that the invoice should be recorded in. Type: integer id The internal identifier for this invoice tax information. Type: integer invoiceId A reference to the related invoice.
